Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:17.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:25.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}震えた瞳は答えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:28.66,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに信じても
